    <p> <img src="/photos/6aa07f673dd1fd4f47e90163b954dd2b.jpg" border="0" alt="Photo" align=right style="margin-left: 1em; width: 200px"> <a href="/dcbpw2014/user/2196">John Anderson (&lrm;genehack&lrm;)</a> -  lightning    <!--  -->
